Package model

Class Appointment

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Appointment
  • public class Appointment
extends java.lang.Object
    The Appointment class - blueprint for all Appointment objects. This class contains other objects - Customer, Contact, and User. apptStartLDT and apptEndLDT are String variables that contain a formatted version of the LocalDateTime objects apptStart and apptEnd.
